import React from 'react'
import { Container, Grid, Typography } from '@material-ui/core'

const Banner = () => {
    return (
        <Container>
            <Grid container justifyContent="center">
                <Grid item>
                    <Typography variant="h1">
                        Vincent Good
                    </Typography>
                    <Typography variant="h2">
                        Industrial Enginner
                    </Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item>
                    
                </Grid>
            </Grid>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default Banner
